section.section:
"Police officer" includes:
a member of the Field Enforcement Bureau of the Comptroller's Office;
the State Fire Marshal or a deputy State fire marshal;
an investigator of the Internal Investigative Unit of the Department;
a Montgomery County fire and explosive investigator as defined in § 2-208.1 of the Criminal Procedure Article;
an Anne Arundel County or City of Annapolis fire and explosive investigator as defined in § 2-208.2 of the Criminal Procedure Article;
a Prince George's County fire and explosive investigator as defined in § 2-208.3 of the Criminal Procedure Article;
a Worcester County fire and explosive investigator as defined in § 2-208.4 of the Criminal Procedure Article; and
a City of Hagerstown fire and explosive investigator as defined in § 2-208.5 of the Criminal Procedure Article.
